creator: Toyota Tsusho Asia Pacific
descriptionHtml:
Convenience
Forget to lock your car? Is the interior of your vehicle too warm?
My Drive allows you to check if the doors of your vehicle are unlocked and a simple hold button can lock it even at miles away.
You don't have to worry anymore if you park at an open space carpark without a shelter - My Drive can start your vehicle engine remotely and by the time you arrive it will be cool and comfortable.

Monitor
Checking your vehicle statistics has never been easier.
My Drive provides a list of information about your vehicle and you can check the historical data and performance any time.

Notification
Get real time notification about the status of your car.
Worried about your children using your vehicle? Did someone tow or bump into your vehicle?
Set geo-fencing parameters easily on your smartphone.
Receive live notifications about the information and whereabouts of your vehicle.

United Arab Emirates, Kingdom of Bahrain.
This version of My Drive Telematics is applicable for Landcruiser 2020MY onwards and Prado 2020MY onwards.
descriptionShort: My Drive allows users to control their Toyota vehicles remotely via smartphones.
